### 1-D — Diagnoses accuracy chart makes 30 separate database calls
**Severity:** 🟡 Performance (admin-side only)

**What the admin sees:**
The accuracy chart in the Diagnoses tab loads slowly. Each of the 30 days it displays requires its own separate round-trip to the database.

**What the farmer sees:**
Indirectly — if the server is busy processing 30 DB calls for the admin chart, it may slow down farmer API responses.

**Root cause:** `GET /api/admin/diagnoses/meta/accuracy-chart` uses `Promise.all(Array.from({length: 30}, async (_, i) => ...supabase.from('scans')...))` — 30 individual queries instead of one date-range query with grouping.

**Fix status:** 🟠 Open

**Files:** `backend/routes/admin/diagnoses.js` L52–68

