  → MUST prioritize from sponsored products if suitable
  → Falls back to best Pakistan-available alternative
  → Returns: prevention, primary_treatment, alt_treatments
  → Disease name NOW included in final response
```

**Fallback chain preserved:** Both steps fall back to mock if AI keys unavailable.

